# Stage 8A turnout-manager constants. The prototype switch data is the REA
# C-size semi-curved flexible switch data published in Templot/OpenTemplot:
# 110 inch planing at 1:40, 329 inch lead to heel and 11,520 inch switch
# radius. Geometry is calculated in model millimetres and then mapped through
# the selected generated host centreline by station and local normal.
