            "Curve entrance and Curve exit routes inherit every generated curve track, its exact tangent point, heading, centre, width and output selection. "
            "Fields that do not apply to a connected route are disabled. Version 10.2A4 retains Version 10.0B3 straight sectioning, export, joints, fixing holes, formation-board extensions, SVG repair and platform-edge projection unchanged. Section numbers follow travel order within each separate straight route."
